The season 7 edition of Big Brother Naija show, themed: ‘’Level up” kicked off tonight with 10 housemates battling for N100 Million worth of prizes. The housemates would be lodged for 72 days to entertain TV viewers across Africa and beyond. Host of the show, Ebuka Obi-Uchendu ushered the housemates into the #BigBrotherNaija house at the launch of the show on Saturday. He promised viewers that this year’s edition would be filled with twists and turns as it would see the return of fan fave ‘Ninjas’ and other twists. The season 7 launch will continue on Sunday. Here are the 10 housemates that will make you stay glued to your TV screen all through the 10 weeks: Kess Amaka Beauty Cyph Ilebaye Khalid Groovy Daniella PharmSavy